eshmun.expression.visitor

Interface Visitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FillDocumentVisitor, GeneralVariableListerVisitor, GreatestSubFormulaListerVisitor, PreFixStringVisitor, ProcessIndicesListerVisitor, SetValuationVisitor, VariableListerVisitor, VisitorAdapter

    public interface Visitor
    Standard Visitor Pattern, Visitors should implement this interface fully.

    If you want to implement a visitor for AbstractExpression and certain sub-types use VisitorAdapter.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kinan Dak Al Bab
    See Also:
    Visitable, VisitorAdapter, AbstractExpression
